1
00:00:04,038 --> 00:00:07,014
“You should love God with
your whole heart, your soul, etc.”

2
00:00:07,430 --> 00:00:11,556
All right, good. And that God,
what does he look like?

3
00:00:11,784 --> 00:00:14,024
[God’s Facebook Profile]

4
00:00:14,024 --> 00:00:15,937
Is he alone?

5
00:00:15,937 --> 00:00:18,127
What does he do?

6
00:00:18,127 --> 00:00:20,214
Where does he live?

7
00:00:21,246 --> 00:00:25,338
That seems to be
a natural question.

8
00:00:25,338 --> 00:00:27,760
This God that we should love
with our whole heart

9
00:00:27,760 --> 00:00:33,204
and soul and everything,
do you have a picture of him?

10
00:00:33,204 --> 00:00:34,879
Show me
what he looks like.

11
00:00:34,879 --> 00:00:37,658
If I said,
“There’s this girl, or guy,

12
00:00:37,658 --> 00:00:40,069
and you’re gonna love them
with your whole heart and soul”,

13
00:00:40,069 --> 00:00:42,527
and the first thing …
you go, “Can I see ’em?”

14
00:00:42,527 --> 00:00:46,574
“Well, no, 
that would be offensive.”

15
00:00:46,574 --> 00:00:47,769
[Laughing]

16
00:00:52,679 --> 00:01:00,485
I mean, it’s common sense.
Why is it called “FACEbook”?

17
00:01:00,485 --> 00:01:02,204
Why?

18
00:01:02,204 --> 00:01:04,988
Does it have 
anything to do with faces?

19
00:01:04,988 --> 00:01:07,950
Maybe?
Looking at faces?

20
00:01:07,950 --> 00:01:12,133
And saying, “I like this face,
and this one I don’t like as much”?

21
00:01:12,501 --> 00:01:18,671
So people, they want a social network
with God, but no pictures.

22
00:01:20,331 --> 00:01:21,902
Why?

23
00:01:22,979 --> 00:01:25,278
Why are they afraid?

24
00:01:25,278 --> 00:01:28,495
Is God married?
Does He have a girlfriend?

25
00:01:28,510 --> 00:01:31,753
Is He in a relationship?

26
00:01:31,753 --> 00:01:34,640
[Laughing]

27
00:01:34,640 --> 00:01:38,199
Relationship status: 
Complicated.

